parts.text:
```json
{
  "application": "PET_Normalization",
  "details": {
    "software": [
      "bash",
      "mri_binarize",
      "matlab",
      "qsub"
    ],
    "resources": [
      "FreeSurfer",
      "MATLAB",
      "cluster (optional)"
    ],
    "dependencies": [
      "CBIG_CODE_DIR",
      "CBIG_MMLDA_normalize_cerebellum_gm"
    ],
    "description": "This script normalizes PET images with respect to the average cerebellum gray matter (GM) value.",
    "input": [
      "id_list (text file with subject IDs)",
      "PET_in_T1.nii.gz (PET image in T1 space)",
      "aparc+aseg.mgz (FreeSurfer segmentation)"
    ],
    "output": [
      "PET_in_T1_NormCere.nii.gz (normalized PET image)",
      "mask_T1_cerebellum_gm.nii.gz (cerebellum GM mask)"
    ]
  }
}
```
